From 31eb2db8ca9faaaa06f971129eda3a2459a0e508 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vasu Bhatia <git@vbh.ai>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:25:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 8/9] eink: intercept KEYCODE_REFRESH with gesture detection
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add EinkGestureDetector inside PhoneWindowManager to intercept the
MP01 physical e-ink button (KEYCODE_REFRESH). Resolves single, double,
and long press — timing windows configurable via Settings.System.
Direct actions (FORCE_REFRESH, CYCLE_MODE, step controls) are executed
inline via EinkManagerService; OPEN_CENTER and preset application are
delegated to SystemUI via a targeted broadcast.

Change-Id: I18250918e5518a7bf923e3999c1dee0d72c6e514
---
